{"tid":722180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應停建出租公屋👋🏼","createTime":"2018-06-29T09:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T14:00:01.000Z","uid":2679,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25f0f58da7261d5a2b489895d0aacaa2fbedc404","tid":722180,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"新移民/蝻就平租住新樓 <br />\n香港本土陀地就要比錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔否認有一定既本地窮人要住<br />\n但唔代表佢一定有新樓住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將所有新建出租公屋<br />\n變做綠置居 再加折扣賣<br />\n等啲新界人可以買市區樓<br />\n吉出黎既公屋 就拎比班新移民去新界住<br />\n<br />\n順便唔洗再出現啲新移民村<br />\n逼班新移民去廢老村 <br />\n唔講白話唔得 仲可以逼佢地融入香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前777想咁做 班賤畜社工話對新移民唔公平<br />\n問點解等咁多年要住舊樓<br />\n因為你班撚樣有大陸唔住落黎呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6834cbc86c32d33f55b52de76b02d64c0e8ec9","tid":722180,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dee7e1074f98d3605eb8aa02c4437163fb4b44","tid":722180,"uid":27675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"咪又係狗噏"},{"pid":"d8aa421ab7999bbbefd52f2ac58bdc2e62ad702e","tid":722180,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4dee7e1074f98d3605eb8aa02c4437163fb4b44","tid":722180,"uid":27675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"咪又係狗噏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"佢果陣話要80萬間封頂<br />\n我唔知點解啲垃圾左膠同社工係到屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a57af9280f1b316c1f59326f4a87eaba1e65444","tid":722180,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/t